---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SecondBrainGraph from '../../components/SecondBrainGraph.astro';
import graphData from '../../data/second-brain.json';
---

<BaseLayout title="第二大脑" description="把 Ryan 在 Obsidian 里留下的想法整理成一张可探索的知识图谱。" lang="zh" path="second-brain">
  <div class="second-brain-home">
    <section class="page-head second-brain-head">
      <div class="eyebrow">Second Brain / {graphData.source}</div>
      <h1>把零散想法，变成一张可以漫游的地图。</h1>
      <p class="lead">这里记录不一定成熟、但值得保留的想法。每个节点是一篇笔记，目录、主题、标签和笔记之间的手工链接共同组成它的邻域。</p>
    </section>

    <nav class="brain-view-switch" aria-label="第二大脑视图">
      <a class="is-active" href="/second-brain/">思想星系</a>
      <a href="/second-brain/timeline/">时间长河</a>
    </nav>

    <section class="section second-brain-intro">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">不是只有 tag</div>
        <h2>先写，再让关系慢慢长出来。</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="muted">旧笔记没有标签也没关系：初版会根据原有目录和正文主题建立基础连接；以后在 Obsidian 中补充 <code>#tag</code> 或 <code>[[笔记链接]]</code>，同步时图谱会自动变得更精确。</p>
    </section>

    <SecondBrainGraph lang="zh" />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
